<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="525" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="6.[1374,2580,1442,1866]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1376,1726,1714,1747]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. Local people hunt the Arfak Ring-tailed Possum for food, and suitable forest habitat has been lost through conversion to cultivated land.
</paragraph>
